  "page": "Sam Salt",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Sam Salt</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a> <small>(claimant)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a> <small>(claimed)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sam Salt</b> was a pretender <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a> who claimed descent from the black line, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sam_Salt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a> was murdered at <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> by his <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_wife\" title=\"Salt wife\">salt wife</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tess\" title=\"Tess\">Tess</a>. In the bloody <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands_succession_struggle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron Islands succession struggle\">struggle for succession</a> that ensued on the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> between his salt sons, sisters, and cousins, Sam Salt emerged as a pretender.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sam_Salt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Template:Lords of the Iron Islands\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Lords of the Iron Islands (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lords of the Iron Islands</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Official succession<br />From <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Vickon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Vickon Greyjoy\">Vickon</a> (2-33)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Goren_Greyjoy\" title=\"Goren Greyjoy\">Goren</a> (33-?)</li>\n<li>Dalton's father (≤113-128)<sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton</a> (128-133)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Toron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Toron Greyjoy\">Toron</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Alton Greyjoy\">Alton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torwyn_Greyjoy\" title=\"Torwyn Greyjoy\">Torwyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loron_Greyjoy_(lord)\" title=\"Loron Greyjoy (lord)\">Loron</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dagon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dagon Greyjoy\">Dagon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quellon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Quellon Greyjoy\">Quellon</a> (?-283)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon</a> (283-299)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron</a> (299-Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Claimants to the Seastone Chair</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy_(son_of_Dalton)\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy (son of Dalton)\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sam Salt</a> (133-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> (299-Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup> Lord Dalton's father is known to have been the heir of Pyke when Dalton was young. Therefore he could not have been Lord of the Iron Islands before 113 AC, the year of Dalton's birth.</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404042703\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.076 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.256 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 796/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 17520/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16750/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4333/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 685/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.34 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  241.214      1 -total\n 91.68%  221.137      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 90.85%  219.145      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.74%   25.895     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.61%   11.116      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.26%   10.283      1 Template:Lords_of_the_Iron_Islands\n  4.00%    9.653      1 Template:Navbox\n  1.75%    4.210      1 Template:Ref\n  1